ere We Are》</a>中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-foo-fighters-powerful-10-minute-single-the-teacher-3449591">《The Teacher》，</a>然后以《Everlong》结束了当晚的演出。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nova-twins">Nova Twins</a>的开场表演之后，该乐队登上了舞台。</p><p>请在此处查看精选视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="喷火战机 - Bridge Burning (Live) 达拉斯, TX 5-1-24" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-st61bKn1dQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="喷火战机 - The Glass (现场) 达拉斯, TX 5-1-24" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ojSQByrHj00?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Foo Fighters 德克萨斯州达拉斯活动扳手 5/1/2024 Dave Grohl" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dPFcSEDcfbc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="喷火战机 - Everlong - 德克萨斯州达拉斯 - 05/01/24" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZBIJ6UZn3o8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="喷火战机现场 - 达拉斯 - 5.1.2024 - Aurora" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ngMGlwmT37A?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; 